heat kills.

235
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:22,550
It is an effective household water
treatment process, effective against

236
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:26,840
all classes of pathogens whether boiling
or pasteurization is used.

237
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,760
Boiling is very widespread.

238
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:34,210
It is the most commonly practiced of the
HWTS options.

239
00:15:34,210 --> 00:15:38,490
But recontamination of boiled water is
also very widespread.

240
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:44,010
Pasteurization works well technically, but
is much less widely applied.
